 Zhihua Wen, Zhiliang Tian, <b>Zexin Jian</b>, Zhen Huang, Pei Ke, Yifu Gao, Minlie Huang, Dongsheng Li.</font></font>\n\n- <font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4><code>ACL 2023</code> <a href=\"https://aclanthology.org/2023.findings-acl.530.pdf\">GRACE: Gradient-guided Controllable Retrieval for Augmenting Attribute-based Text Generation</a>, Zhihua Wen, Zhiliang Tian, Zhen Huang, Yuxin Yang, <b>Zexin Jian</b>, Changjian Wang, Dongsheng Li.</font></font>\n\n<br/>\n\n## 📖 Experience\n### 😊 Education\n- <font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4><i>2021.09 - 2025.06</i>, School of Computer Science, <b>National University of Defense Technology</b>, Changsha, China.</font></font>\n\n<br/>\n\n### 👩‍🏫 Teaching Experience\n- <font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4><b>National University of Defense Technology</b></font></font>\n  - <font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4>TA for Operating System, Fall 2024;</font></font>\n  - <font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4>TA for College Computing Fundamentals, Fall 2023;</font></font>\n  - <font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4>TA for Operating System, Fall 2023;</font></font> \n  - <font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4>TA for C++ Programming, Spring 2023;</font></font>\n  - <font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4>TA for C++ Programming, Fall 2022.</font></font>","source":"about.md","raw":"---\ntitle: \"About Me\"\ncover: assets/about.png\ncoverWidth: 894\ncoverHeight: 504\nexcerpt: \"\"\nauthor_profile: true\npermalink: /about.html\n---\n\n<font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4>Welcome! I am an undergraduate student at Computer College, <b>National University of Defense Technology (国防科技大学计算机学院). </b></font></font>\n\n<font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4>My research interest includes <b>MLSys (Operating System, Compiler and so on) and Large Language Models (LLM). </b></font></font>\n\n<font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4>If you are seeking any form of academic cooperation, please feel free to email me at <a href=\"\">zexinjian@foxmail.com</a>. </font></font>\n\n## 🔥 News\n\n- <font face=\"楷书\"><font size=4><i>2024.09</i